SunUO README
============

(c) 2005-2007 Max Kellermann <max@duempel.org>

$Id$


What is SunUO?
--------------

SunUO is a free Ultima Online server, based on RunUO.


Getting SunUO
-------------

You can download SunUO on the home page:

 http://www.sunuo.org/


Installation and Configuration
------------------------------

Most of the documentation has moved to another file written in
DocBook. There is an online version:

 http://www.sunuo.org/doc/sunuo.html


For the impatient
-----------------

1. unpack the SunUO binary zip file

2. edit "etc/sunuo.xml" and enter the correct UO client data path

3. start "run.bat" (Windows/.NET) or "run.sh" (Linux/Mono)


